# Cloudflare Pages — SPA fallback, but exclude /api/* so a mis-pointed
# frontend doesn't silently receive index.html (HTTP 200) in place of a
# proper 404. Without this, axios treats the SPA shell as a JSON body
# and every page breaks with "s?.filter is not a function" downstream.
/api/*    /api/:splat    404
/*        /index.html    200
